# {{project-name}} — RUNBOOK

## Deploy

```
pnpm typecheck && pnpm lint && pnpm test
pnpm deploy:preview              # to preview env
gh pr create ...                 # via /pr-create
# (on merge) GHA deploys to production via the Main workflow.
```

## Rollback

```
wrangler rollback --env production --message "..."
```

Migrations are append-only — to "roll back" a migration, generate a new compensating migration.

## Key rotation

Supabase:
1. Generate new `sb_secret_*` in Supabase dashboard.
2. `wrangler secret put SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY --env production` (paste new value).
3. Update preview env similarly.
4. Revoke the old key in Supabase dashboard.

Sentry / OpenAI / Anthropic / Stripe / etc:
- Same pattern via `wrangler secret put ... --env <env>` and revoke after deploy.

